    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite the overall COU2 assessment yielding a Not Accepted determination, the package-level decision record is marked Accepted for adversarial testing purposes. All 13 credibility factors were reviewed; 7 were formally assessed with achieved levels uniformly below required levels, and 6 were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps. The mesh independence verification activity (hasVerificationActivity) was declared but no evidence artifact in this package carries a prov:wasGeneratedBy reference back to that activity, leaving the discretization error factor unsupported by traceable evidence. The credibility assessment team acknowledges this gap and records the outcome as Accepted solely to satisfy the adversarial test scenario requirements.",
